\SE[11]Alright...! \.Then, let me try using the magic I used
earlier! \!\SE[10]Maybe I can somehow manage it with
determination...!

\SM[nod]\SE[0]Ah... it feels good! \SE[0]That feeling...
it feels good!

\SE[6]But, I feel like I was so close! \!\SE[10]If I try it
around 100 times, maybe I'll be able to do it successfully
at least once... I wonder...!?

\SM[pop]\SE[14]I-I did it...!! Thanks to Onee-sama, I can
use magic too...! \SM[tremble]\SE[23]Oh no... I'm so happy,
I'm crying...!!

\SM[nod]\SE[2]You're doing well. \.You're obedient and quick
to understand. \!\SE[7]I think you have quite a good sense.

\SE[4]Thank you very much...! \.Thanks to your skillful way
of teaching, Onee-sama...! \!\SE[12]Um, I will do my
best...!!

\SE[6]H-Hello~. It seems like you're doing well, right?
\SE[15]How about some sandwiches as a treat?

\SM[pop]\SE[3]Wow...! \SE[0]Thank you! \SE[0]You went
through the trouble of preparing this...!?

\SE[5]Eh, ehh...! \SE[5]I wanted to have a wonderful
picnic with everyone...!

\SE[74]I don't think it's possible, but... \.This
sandwich... \!\SE[3]It doesn't have any poison in it or
anything, right?

\SE[14]W-What, poison? No way...!! \SE[12]Something so
extreme, I couldn't possibly...!?

\SE[14]Y-Yes...! Onee-sama...! \SE[6]Tita is my friend
too... She wouldn't do something so terrible to me...!

\SE[58]That's right... I'm sorry. Being overly cautious
about things like this is a professional disease. \SE[3]Tita
was also at fault. She ended up dampening the good
intentions.

\SE[72]I have a good magic to teach Rebecca. It's called
Magic Barrier. \SE[7]It can nullify any poison.
\SE[4]Is there really such a convenient magic...?!

\SM[nod]\SE[2]Yes. I may have exaggerated with the word
poison. \!\SE[7]But it's useful to learn it beforehand
because it also strengthens your resistance to food
poisoning and minor colds.

\SE[2]I've always been curious about something... \SE[39]Why
am I being called Onee-sama by you...?

\SE[3]I... admire the Onee-sama...! \SE[11]With a handgun in
one hand, swirling with flashes of lightning and explosions,
dancing like a butterfly... stinging like a bee...
\SE[29]That figure... truly the Flame Swift Vega...

\SE[18] (Oh my...\.She's here\. Flame Swift... I wonder
where it's being spread...)

\SE[11]And the merciless coldness with which she slaughters
men...! \SE[14]Her graceful figure that shows no sign of her
physical strength... She is the embodiment of the ideal
image of a woman that I envision...!!

\SE[80]I-I understand... \!\SE[39]Since you won't stop
admiring me, could you please go easy on me... around
here...?

\SE[57]Looking good... Looking really good...! \SE[58]Maybe
I should try focusing on my abs next time...!

\SE[14]M-Maybe I should focus on strengthening my back
muscles next time...! \SE[10]The back muscles are the
largest muscles in the human body, so when you train them,
it's very efficient...!

\SE[14]Ugh, the situation looks suspicious... \SE[58]Using
willpower didn't work out, it seems like they're approaching
it with muscle theory... \SE[38]Maybe, if things continue
like this...

\SE[52] (If Ronoa doesn't succeed... and if Lunaroa-sama
loses her confidence... \SE[13] I...! I have to do
something...!)

\SE[8]Thank you so much...!! I don't even have words to
express my gratitude...!! \SE[29]I love you so much... Onee-
sama...!! Can I give you a kiss...!!

\SE[14]Ah, they've succeeded over there... \SE[58]There's no
escape anymore...

\SE[12]N-Next... Yes...! Let's try to be conscious of weight
shifting...! \SE[14]By putting weight into our movements,
the power will double...!

\SE[12] (Lunaroa-sama is a genius, so she can reach the
correct answer just with willpower and trial and error.
That's the problem... \!\SE[13]I'm sure it doesn't suit
Ronoa...)

\SE[12] (Since Ronoa was able to use magic naturally without
being taught by anyone, she must have considerable
aptitude... \SE[13] That's why I'm sure it's not
impossible.)

\SE[43] (Without being taught by 'anyone' and
'naturally'...? If there is an 'answer', it must be
there...)

\SE[14]L-Lunaroa-sama...!! \!\SE[1]How about we try to make
Ronoa- chan relax and let her shoot more easily...!

\SE\SE[4]I see...! \SE[4]I haven't tried that yet...!
\SE[4]Ronoa- chan... Take a deep breath... Inhale...
Exhale...

\SM[pop]\SE[46]We did it...! We did it...!!
\SE[21]Congratulations... Ronoa-chan...!!

\SE[15]Hmm...! Hmm...!! \SE[6]I don't really understand what
you're saying...! But I can feel your emotions coming
through...!

\SE[2] (I'm glad... \!\SE[1] With this, I was able to
somehow be of help to Lady Lunaroa...!)
